@sig 30b74887
@vars s=workspaceRoot,a=__dirname,p=selfRoot,c=wsArg
export setRoots(roots)→uri.startsWith,uri.slice,console.error|set workspace root dirs from MCP client (file:// URI or path)
export getWorkspaceRoot()→process.cwd|return first workspace root or cwd fallback
export resolvePath(inputPath)→getWorkspaceRoot,isAbsolute,resolve,resolved.startsWith|resolve relative path to absolute, enforce workspace boundary
PATTERNS: workspace roots set once via MCP initialize|resolvePath prevents directory traversal attacks
EDGE_CASES: file:// URIs auto-stripped to path|absolute paths outside workspace rejected|empty roots fall back to process.cwd()
